%I A395462 #14 May 27 2026 00:24:38
%S A395462 0,4,76,5780,1382640,946033915,1860478140351
%N A395462 Number of undirected self-avoiding paths in the mod n square grid graph, reduced for symmetry (with rotations, reflections, and translations not counted as distinct).
%C A395462 Here a "mod n square grid graph" is a n X n graph with wrapping allowed, e.g., a path can make a 1 unit step between the left and the right edge (same row) or the top and the bottom edge (same column) of the graph.
%C A395462 Excludes 0 length paths; including them increases each term by 1.
%e A395462 a(2) = 4:
%e A395462   X--X   X--+   X--+     X--+
%e A395462             |      |        |
%e A395462             X   X--+   ..X  +..
%Y A395462 Cf. A396337 (directed), A394065 (wrapping disallowed).
%K A395462 nonn,walk,hard,more,new
%O A395462 1,2
%A A395462 _Charles L. Hohn_, May 22 2026
